Posted By: Brian
All cards are framed backed.  Some cards have the factory ink mark.  Scans available on request (I will post over the next few days).  Great opportunity to get a high grade type (issue or team), or if you are crazy enough to go for the set possibly fill in your list.


Prices are for insured delivery paid by check or money order.  I will respond to requests/commitments by email timestamps (three25hits@yahoo.com).  Response times may very over the next few days due to life happening. 

Trades for equally scarce/condition sensitive prewar will be considered; especially 1911 Obaks in SGC 80 or better that I need. 

Thanks,
Brian
